<h1>恋</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#000099;">liàn</span><span class=alesi>(lian4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 恋 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 恋</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/love" style="color:black;">love</a>; <a href="/dictionary/long" style="color:black;">long</a> <a href="/dictionary/for" style="color:black;">for</a>, yearn for; love</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 10<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 10 strokes: <a href="/character/能" title="neng2: to be able; can, permitted to; ability">能</a>, <a href="/character/家" title="jia1: house, home, residence; family">家</a>, <a href="/character/都" title="dou1: metropolis, capital; all, the whole; elegant, refined">都</a>, <a href="/character/起" title="qi3: rise, stand up; go up; begin">起</a>, <a href="/character/部" title="bu4: part, division, section">部</a>, <a href="/character/样" title="yang4: shape, form, pattern, style">样</a>, <a href="/character/高" title="gao1: high, tall; lofty, elevated">高</a>, <a href="/character/被" title="">被</a>, <a href="/character/特" title="te4: special, unique, distinguished">特</a>, <a href="/character/海" title="hai3: sea, ocean; maritime">海</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/心" title="Kangxi radical 61">心</a>&nbsp;61.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 5 <br><small>Other HSK 5 characters: <a href="/character/吓" title="xia4: scare, frighten; intimidate">吓</a>, <a href="/character/眉" title="mei2: eyebrows; upper margin of book">眉</a>, <a href="/character/辞" title="ci2: words, speech, expression, phrase">辞</a>, <a href="/character/腰" title="yao1: waist; kidney">腰</a>, <a href="/character/尺" title="">尺</a>, <a href="/character/贴" title="tie1: paste to, stick on; attached to">贴</a>, <a href="/character/辈" title="bei4: generation, lifetime; class">辈</a>, <a href="/character/赏" title="shang3: reward, grant, bestow; appreciate">赏</a>, <a href="/character/骂" title="ma4: accuse, blame, curse, scold">骂</a>, <a href="/character/滑" title="hua2: slip, slide; slippery, polished">滑</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-5" title="List of HSK 5 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 5 char